   Alex Abdalla Sr., 47, and Juan Rosado, 19, must serve at least
30 years before they can be eligible for parole.
   During sentencing Thursday, Superior Court Judge Barnett Hoffman
said the pair acted like ``a bunch of jackals attacking a
carcass.'' Hoffman said they beat and kicked Mario Santos, 25,
although he lay unconscious on the ground.
