the announcement.
   The ethics panel said Friday it will probe the activities of
Majority Whip Alan Cranston, D-Calif.; Banking Committee Chairman
Donald W. Riegle, Jr., D-Mich.; John McCain, R-Ariz.; Dennis
DeConcini, D-Ariz., and John Glenn, D-Ohio.
